description.narrative: The government has made a strong commitment to the development of alternative care through the promulgation of new decrees promoting family care for children in danger. The new decrees provide a new legal framework for improving the care of children at risk and more particularly on the de-institutionalization of children in line with Guidelines for the alternative care of children.This progress in the legislative framework of the child protection system in Algeria gives the opportunity to achieve new results for children. | Status:Constrained | As-of Date:26/12/2019
